# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docker build context exclusions.
#
# The Dockerfile does `COPY . .`. Without this file, every local secret and
# build artifact on disk is copied into an image layer — where it survives
# even if a later layer deletes it, and ships to anyone who pulls the image.
# Order matters: the secret rules below are NOT negated anywhere.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Secrets — the reason this file is non-negotiable ──────────────────────
# `.env` and `.env.production` are gitignored and hold REAL credentials
# (Paystack live keys, AWS keys, JWT secrets, ENCRYPTION_KEY). Runtime config
# is injected as environment variables by the platform, never baked in.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
.npmrc.local
secrets/
**/*.secret

# ── VCS & CI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# `.git` also leaks history (including any secret ever committed) and busts
# the layer cache on every commit.
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github

# ── Dependencies & build output ───────────────────────────────────────────
# node_modules is reinstalled inside the image for the correct libc/arch —
# copying host (Windows) modules in would ship broken native bindings
# (bcrypt, sharp).
node_modules
**/node_modules
.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn
.next
out
build
dist
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Test & tooling artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────
coverage
test-results
playwright-report
blob-report
.playwright
e2e/.artifacts
tests
e2e
# `playwright.config.ts` is a root file (so `COPY . .` would otherwise pull it
# into the build stage) but it imports `./e2e/*` — which is excluded above. It
# is test-only and never shipped (the runner stage copies neither it nor e2e/),
# and the production tsconfig excludes it so `next build` no longer type-checks
# it. Dropping it from the context too is belt-and-braces: the build cannot even
# see the file whose `./e2e/dbFixture` import previously broke `docker build`.
playwright.config.ts

# ── Editor / OS noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# ── Docs & local-only config (not needed to build or run) ─────────────────
docs
README.md
*.md
!package.json
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
compose.yaml
docker-compose.yml
docker-compose.*.yml

# ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
